SUB_W11_EVAR_AMYA_LOVE_100_CUT_000_070.text:
Worry not, Lela. Merely plant the seeds.
You are chosen by the god of the Imeru;
the markings on your face serve as proof.

SUB_W11_EVAR_AMYA_EPUIKE_200_CUT_010_050.text:
I mean, I know I only came here to look
for my cat, but Chup's only Soyay is me,
and I want to see it through to the end.
